data.description: Darling curb appeal, this two-story home is located in the desirable Vine Creek community developed by Starlight Homes and Ashton Woods Homes. Backyard gazebo, washer/dryer and refrigerator will all convey with home purchase. Home was recently painted, lightly lived in and well-maintained: 3 bedrooms (all up), 2 1/2 bathrooms and approximately 1645 square feet. Light, bright open floor plan between living, kitchen and dining for today’s casual lifestyle. Stainless steel appliances, granite counters, ample counter and cabinet space. Spacious owner's suite with ensuite bathroom, walk-in closet and plentiful storage. Window blinds and full rain gutters. Wonderfully private backyard with a covered patio and gazebo placed on a cement slab. Neighborhood amenities include a pool with a splash pad, playground, park, hike/bike trails, basketball + volleyball courts, outdoor "gym" and easy access to shopping centers, restaurants and schools. Lake Pflugerville is about 5-miles with a trail, fishing pier, swimming and places for kids + pets to run. Convenient commute with relatively close proximity to 130 making the airport, Tesla, Domain and downtown Austin all manageable on a daily basis.
